choices.text:
not being able to play soccer anymore, but not seeing some of the friends I’ve made back. During this period during COVID-19, it has been hard to communicate with them over the phone and then see them in the few time given we were restricted to meet. But like a sorority sister, one of best qualities we posses is to come together to make sure that one another’s are being taken care of. It might not resolve the whole issue but by coming together we can bring some relief and happiness to others.

-Sahara Yala, Spring 2021 Member
